content.html: We’re celebrating 10 years since @GOVUK launched today with @GDSTeam. Since going live @GOVUK has merged nearly 2,000 separate government websites into one, giving the public consistent, quick and easy access to information, services and guidance when they need it most.
content.value:
We’re celebrating 10 years since @GOVUK launched today with @GDSTeam. 

Since going live @GOVUK has merged nearly 2,000 separate government websites into one, giving the public consistent, quick and easy access to information, services and guidance when they need it most.
